  "text": "For other KSs, which are not part of the LOD cloud (e.g. Wikidata [CITATION_1] ), the proposed framework could still be applied provided that a mapping between the DBpedia KS and the newly explored KS exists. A possible future direction could be to utilise the data from DBpedia, and derive contextual information about entities from the semantic meta-graph of the new KS.",
